// Secrets.xcconfig.example
//
// Copy this file to Secrets.xcconfig (which is gitignored) and fill in your tokens.
// Referenced from Info.plist via $(MBX_ACCESS_TOKEN).
//
// 1. Mapbox public token (pk.…) — get one at https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
//    Recommended: restrict by bundle ID (e.g. eu.YOURNAME.tripperdashpp) for safety.
MBX_ACCESS_TOKEN = pk.YOUR_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN_HERE

// 2. Mapbox secret download token (sk.…, scope Downloads:Read) goes in ~/.netrc, NOT here:
//
//    machine api.mapbox.com
//      login mapbox
//      password sk.YOUR_SECRET_DOWNLOAD_TOKEN
//
//    It's only needed at SDK fetch time (SPM resolution), not at runtime.
